    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> and lay the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>green beans </strong>and your <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> in the middle</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and scrunch the edges up to form a tightly sealed parcel, put the parcel on a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Make 2 separate parcels!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1667319574429-x200.jpg",
