            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the greens are cooking, add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 225ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1667319583964-x200.jpg",
