          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Finely slice some of your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds and set aside for garnish</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chilli </strong>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
