            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the greens are done, remove the parcel[s] from the oven and drain away any excess water</p><p>Add them to a bowl with your<strong> toasted sesame oil</strong> and stir to combine – these are your <strong>sesame greens</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
