            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy hoisin lean pork</strong> with the <strong>sesame greens</strong> over the <strong>cooked rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
